data.description: Welcome to Vintage View!!!  This beautiful three bedroom, two bath pool home is available for your viewing pleasure.  Located on a large corner lot with a beautiful circular paver driveway, this home is the perfect home for you! NEW ROOF allowance with full price offer! As you enter the home through the front porch, you will notice the foyer and dining room with beautiful wainscoting, the perfect room for hosting dinner parties! The living room is spacious and has amazing views of the Lanai and pool area. Crown Molding.  Open kitchen plan with lots of storage, built-in microwave &  oven! Eating space in kitchen has lots of room and cozy at the same tome.  Tray ceilings in the primary bedroom, living room, and eating space. The pool area is the real star of the home.  A spacious covered Lanai is the perfect sitting place overlooking the enclosed pool. This is a great swimming pool!  Do you work remotely?  The den is a perfect office with gorgeous built-in wood cabinets and wood flooring.  In-ceiling speakers throughout the house. Primary bedroom has sliding doors out to the Lanai.  Jack & Jill walk-in closets featuring California Closet storage . Primary bath has dual vanities, toilet room, and a shower with separate tub.  Split bedroom plan. Larger two car garage, perfect for extra storage.  Make you appointment to see this beautiful home today!!!
